football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.907273349174553e-29, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Australia and New Zealand, the Asian outfit demonstrated multiple ways it can earn results - with majority possession or just waiting for its moment and hitting the opposition on a quick counter.\", \"from\": 11073, \"to\": 11271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11076, \"end\": 11085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.118853357177109e-47, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11090, \"end\": 11101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.534622302285477e-16, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11107, \"end\": 11112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.143233555441916e-16, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan got the best of North Korea over two legs, 2-1, in late February to qualify.\", \"from\": 11272, \"to\": 11354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11272, \"end\": 11277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.907273349174553e-29, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11294, \"end\": 11305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999952233338, \"rank\": 4.776359595701873e-09, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the team's four players on this Olympic roster under 21, Aoba Fujino scored the winner in the second leg.\", \"from\": 11355, \"to\": 11467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11419, \"end\": 11423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambae_Island\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.512003984856021e-18, \"text\": \"Aoba\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambae_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambae_Island\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan was drawn into the toughest group of the tournament, in our opinion,Group Cwith Spain, Brazil, and Nigeria.\", \"from\": 11469, \"to\": 11582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11469, \"end\": 11474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.907273349174553e-29, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11562, \"end\": 11568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.380297451725968e-23, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11574, \"end\": 11581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.863734372513978e-23, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like any one of those teams, the Asian side is more than capable of topping the group of four.\", \"from\": 11583, \"to\": 11677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11616, \"end\": 11621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.143233555441916e-16, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ikeda's team has an incredibly well-drilled defense with a group of forward players who rely on each other rather than individual talent to find success.\", \"from\": 11678, \"to\": 11831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11678, \"end\": 11683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\", \"score\": 0.9999976303907596, \"rank\": 2.3696151137361485e-06, \"text\": \"Ikeda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe are confident we can show our Nadeshiko style performance, and we promise to play with 100 percent effort,\\\"said coach Ikeda.\", \"from\": 11833, \"to\": 11963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11957, \"end\": 11962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\", \"score\": 0.9999976303907596, \"rank\": 2.3696151137361485e-06, \"text\": \"Ikeda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daisaku_Ikeda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And by playing like this game-by-game I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m sure there will be a medal waiting for us.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Group:AWorld Ranking:2  It has been 28 years since the host of the Olympic Games captured the gold in women's football.\", \"from\": 11964, \"to\": 12175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Herv\\u00c3\\u00a9 Renard and the French national team will look to change that.\", \"from\": 12176, \"to\": 12244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12198, \"end\": 12218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.759662673763648e-13, \"text\": \"French national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In its only two previous appearances in this competition, France finished at least top-six with London 2012 being its best showing - fourth place.\", \"from\": 12245, \"to\": 12391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12303, \"end\": 12309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.699504282819139e-29, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 12341, \"end\": 12352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2396051322207965e-17, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nation's first major piece of silverware continues to escape its grasp.\", \"from\": 12392, \"to\": 12467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the fans behind the players, that could very well change.\", \"from\": 12468, \"to\": 12530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Renard's team is not only talented but extraordinarily experienced with nine of the 18 players above the age of 27.\", \"from\": 12532, \"to\": 12647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyon's Wendie Renard is the rock at the back, sitting behind Grace Geyoro, the metronome of Les Bleues' midfield.\", \"from\": 12648, \"to\": 12761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12648, \"end\": 12652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.074003046895856e-31, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}, {\"begin\": 12655, \"end\": 12668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wendie_Renard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wendie Renard\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wendie_Renard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wendie_Renard\"}, {\"begin\": 12709, \"end\": 12721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Geyoro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grace Geyoro\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Geyoro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Geyoro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody completed more passes into the final third at the most recent World Cup than the Paris Saint-Germain midfielder.\", \"from\": 12762, \"to\": 12881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's attack though is what makes it such a gold medal threat.\", \"from\": 12883, \"to\": 12948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12883, \"end\": 12889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.699504282819139e-29, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All five forwards that Renard named to the team provide their own unique challenge for an opponent's defense.\", \"from\": 12949, \"to\": 13058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team has last season's top two scorers in the Champions League, Kadidiatou Diani and Marie-Antoinette Katoto, a three-time Division 1 F\\u00c3\\u00a9minine leading scorer who was forced to miss the World Cup due to an injury.\", \"from\": 13059, \"to\": 13276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13109, \"end\": 13125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.9709575760686704e-105, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 13127, \"end\": 13143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadidiatou_Diani\", \"score\": 0.9999999999399733, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kadidiatou Diani\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadidiatou_Diani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadidiatou_Diani\"}, {\"begin\": 13148, \"end\": 13171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie-Antoinette_Katoto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marie-Antoinette Katoto\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie-Antoinette_Katoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie-Antoinette_Katoto\"}, {\"begin\": 13186, \"end\": 13196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ligue_1\", \"score\": 0.9999999814790501, \"rank\": 1.8521428663937437e-08, \"text\": \"Division 1\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ligue_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ligue_1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quality does not even end there.\", \"from\": 13277, \"to\": 13313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eug\\u00c3\\u00a9nie Le Sommer, the country's goal scoring extraordinaire, will be making her third appearance at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 13314, \"to\": 13429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13326, \"end\": 13332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Sommer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.166672949825205e-29, \"text\": \"Sommer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Sommer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Sommer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Group:BWorld Ranking:5  It's only been four games into Emma Hayes' tenure but that does not matter - it's go time.\", \"from\": 13431, \"to\": 13545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13486, \"end\": 13496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Hayes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The USWNT sets off into this tournament with a whole lot to prove and with the nation's youngest Olympic roster since 2008.\", \"from\": 13546, \"to\": 13669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13550, \"end\": 13555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2023 was one to forget for U.S. soccer fans.\", \"from\": 13670, \"to\": 13714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The leaf has been turned now.\", \"from\": 13715, \"to\": 13744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This team is onto something new.\", \"from\": 13745, \"to\": 13777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Something exciting.\", \"from\": 13778, \"to\": 13797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not hire one of the world's most well-known winners in club football for nothing.\", \"from\": 13798, \"to\": 13886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a clear goal - bring the U.S. back to the top after hitting rock bottom in Australia and New Zealand.\", \"from\": 13888, \"to\": 13998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13972, \"end\": 13981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.118853357177109e-47, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 13986, \"end\": 13997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.534622302285477e-16, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not rush the process though.\", \"from\": 13999, \"to\": 14030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Practice makes perfect.\", \"from\": 14031, \"to\": 14054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To become the well-oiled machine Hayes intends to create, we are going to see bumps in the road.\", \"from\": 14055, \"to\": 14151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's just learning.\", \"from\": 14152, \"to\": 14173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, no this is not gold medal or bust for this group.\", \"from\": 14174, \"to\": 14227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's more about building a foundation and showing signs of life as the federation was clearly looking at the bigger picture when it hired Hayes.\", \"from\": 14228, \"to\": 14372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get to know Emma Hayes off the field with@sammymewy!Watch/listen below \\u00e2\\u00a4\\u00b5\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008f@WomensGameMIBx@CocaCola  Do not get me wrong, the talent is there for a gold medal run to be in the USWNT's future.\", \"from\": 14374, \"to\": 14567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14386, \"end\": 14396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Hayes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\"}, {\"begin\": 14552, \"end\": 14557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Captain Lindsey Horan is set to take the reins for real this time with Alex Morgan not in the team.\", \"from\": 14568, \"to\": 14667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14576, \"end\": 14589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lindsey Horan\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\"}, {\"begin\": 14639, \"end\": 14650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.049951183080759e-111, \"text\": \"Alex Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hayes' energetic and versatile front three of Mallory Swanson, Trinity Rodman, and Sophia Smith head into this tournament with pressure on their shoulders as finishing is the clear number one issue of this team right now.\", \"from\": 14668, \"to\": 14889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14714, \"end\": 14721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"score\": 0.9999999953324732, \"rank\": 3.9477126188844525e-09, \"text\": \"Mallory\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\"}, {\"begin\": 14722, \"end\": 14729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.2050049331978807e-12, \"text\": \"Swanson\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\"}, {\"begin\": 14731, \"end\": 14745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"}, {\"begin\": 14751, \"end\": 14757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\", \"score\": 0.9999996105871863, \"rank\": 3.8941265935754897e-07, \"text\": \"Sophia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What we are most interested in is the adjustments in game and between games by this new leadership.\", \"from\": 14891, \"to\": 14990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What does it look like?\", \"from\": 14991, \"to\": 15014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will we see a formation change?\", \"from\": 15015, \"to\": 15046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where do these positionally flexible players play?\", \"from\": 15047, \"to\": 15097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will see but what we do know is that the person making these changes is someone who has been the definition of sustained success in club football over the past decade plus.\", \"from\": 15098, \"to\": 15273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Group:CWorld Ranking:1  In our eyes, there is no question who the favorite is.\", \"from\": 15275, \"to\": 15353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain, the reigning world champions, led by Montserrat Tom\\u00c3\\u00a9 are the team to beat.\", \"from\": 15354, \"to\": 15436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15354, \"end\": 15359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.92524547776906e-12, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 15398, \"end\": 15408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montserrat_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995612998699, \"rank\": 4.3870027837632523e-07, \"text\": \"Montserrat\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montserrat_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montserrat_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like on the men's side.\", \"from\": 15437, \"to\": 15465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spanish right now just own international football.\", \"from\": 15466, \"to\": 15520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15470, \"end\": 15477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.8966194628209149, \"rank\": 0.11530034919227383, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shockingly, this is La Roja's first ever Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 15521, \"to\": 15576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if Tom\\u00c3\\u00a9 and company do not reach at least the gold medal match in the nation's first run at it, we'd view it as a disappointment.\", \"from\": 15577, \"to\": 15711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where we are at.\", \"from\": 15712, \"to\": 15735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain's talent is through the roof.\", \"from\": 15737, \"to\": 15772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15737, \"end\": 15742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.92524547776906e-12, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aitana Bonmat\\u00c3\\u00ad, the 2023 Ballon d'Or F\\u00c3\\u00a9minin winner, is the player we will all be keeping a close eye on.\", \"from\": 15773, \"to\": 15880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15773, \"end\": 15779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana\", \"score\": 0.9999983062076147, \"rank\": 1.6937952501655603e-06, \"text\": \"Aitana\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world's most technical midfielder is surrounded by world class players at every position.\", \"